    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As you hit with a weapon attack or unarmed strike, the attack deals an extra [[/r 1d6]] plus your spellcasting ability modifier psychic damage, and the target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or be frightened of you until the end of your next turn or until the spell ends if you choose to maintain concentration on this spell. The frightened target can repeat the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success.</p><p><strong>At Higher Levels</strong>. When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, the extra damage dealt by the attack increases by [[/r 1d6]] for each slot.</p>",
